eback to the place you belong to.”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\">“I was ordered to executed you, the King's reward is sure tempting.”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ac8733e9-b10b-47f9-9463-54b250162c8b_298d9732-c173-48ee-b5f7-0882278b6f24.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">Sequel(Postntr): <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/99aec6ca-fe38-40c6-8093-a0c7f9203adc_character-to-you-whom-we-betray-the-tale-of-redemption-and-revenge\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">To you whom we betray — the tale of redemption and revenge</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9d89697b-34c7-4ac0-9a18-7e9f9ff1699e_character-muu-un-faithful-fairy\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">[Muu Route]</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e819cd8e-3719-4f65-8d88-f0772144ba9a\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">[Good ending]</a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Variation:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ac8733e9-b10b-47f9-9463-54b250162c8b_f9ca0697-b556-4887-8e9f-0b4ddcb7472c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ac8733e9-b10b-47f9-9463-54b250162c8b_3c0e3db3-3a9c-4cd2-843f-37d02c6f82d6.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ac8733e9-b10b-47f9-9463-54b250162c8b_aea90c9d-e542-482e-8fd1-f9e606a7b